snippet.title: Ova Magica - Features Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience a colorful farm game inspired by the classics! Train cute blob creatures, take care of your farm and make friends with the people of Clover Town. 



Source: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jQvP5eDdOzk


Ova Magica on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/claudiathedev/ova-magica


Ova Magica on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1299170/Ova_Magica/
